{"tid":2126144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如何解決香港醫療系統負荷問題","createTime":"2020-07-26T16:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T07:23:58.000Z","uid":177235,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea41b85affc597572400c81b507f8dca9efba633","tid":2126144,"uid":177235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T16:18:14.000Z","msg":"偉大嘅祖国一直零感染，之前興建嘅方舱医院...唔用真係好浪費～ 又要勞煩一半內地嘅医护人員離鄉別井，隨時客死異鄉，唔係太好嘅... <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我建議以<span class=\"blue\">自願形式</span>將香港嘅病人送到大湾区醫治，等香港人感受祖国嘅溫暖、大湾区嘅威力。<span class=\"orange\">香港咁多人支持政府、熱愛祖国，咁呢個數目應該唔細啦...</span> 相信病人就算訓喺ICU都會彈起身應承，分享呢份喜悅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果班染病嘅藍絲唔肯舉手嘅，仲邊有資格話自己愛国呢？所以佢地一定會應承！香港警察就更應該把握機會認識內地發達嘅医疗系統～  所以政府快啲推行啦，唔推就中圈套㗎喇！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ddc0e05461cd69ae7b8f5d1953b0ccd1b2e3b7a","tid":2126144,"uid":205469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T16:19:55.000Z","msg":"要求染病的香港警察身先士卒前往大灣區接受治療<br />\n以展示其愛國情操"},{"pid":"dd8d367f171b6560fd125cdf86f8ba803e49e93f","tid":2126144,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T16:22:35.000Z","msg":"仲以為你有新片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5abcbf7459f28e88c453a7fa296ffb44612c8803","tid":2126144,"uid":177235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd8d367f171b6560fd125cdf86f8ba803e49e93f","tid":2126144,"uid":195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T16:22:35.000Z","msg":"仲以為你有新片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"人在香港係多啲限制㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f532a25ead8f61c205d2bdf2b74e5466ad22837","tid":2126144,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T02:47:28.000Z","msg":"染病警察同慶回歸群組可以試下上海深圳醫護<i